# Frontend Conventions

- Pages in `frontend/src/pages/`, shared components in `frontend/src/components/`.
- API calls via `frontend/src/api/client.js` — parse errors from `{ error }` or `{ errors }`.
- Show user-visible error messages from API responses; do not swallow 422 state machine errors.
- Status transition buttons: only render `getAllowedTransitions(currentStatus)` options.
- Use React Router for navigation. Keep forms controlled with local state.
